## media

media are customizable. 'image' and 'video' are built-in. they must appear on their own line

image[A fire]https://web.site/img.jpg
shortcut for the above: ![xyz]xyz
video[]http://web.site/vid.mp4

# lists

[
lists are easy to type, no line prefixes needed
one item goes on each line. Bold/italic etc. are processed
To add sub-lists, just nest lists
this is an ordered list:
